Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:18.34,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I have a big gun, I took it from my Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:21.79,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Sick with Justice, I just wanna feel you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:25.20,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm your angel, only a ring away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:28.55,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You make me violate you, no matter who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:38.67,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's all up to you, no one lives forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:42.26,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Been burn in the hell, by all those pigs out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.34,0:00:45.53,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's always been hell, from when I was born...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:48.72,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}They make me violate them, no matter who they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.72,0:00:52.26,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs79}Get down on your knees! Get a good head on your shoulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:55.69,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}If it's for your guys, go to the end of the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.69,0:00:59.00,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Do what you think, give it with dedication...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:02.27,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'll put out your misery!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:05.67,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You made a mess! For Christ sakes, this rotten world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:09.10,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Shit out of luck! Go with my vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:12.54,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Light up the fire! Right on the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:15.90,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Weapon... I have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:24.48,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Weapon... I have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.33,0:02:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's this joke I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.47,0:02:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many Polaks does it take\Nto change a light bulb?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.11,0:02:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One to hold the light bulb,\Nninety-nine to turn the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.02,0:02:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.45,0:02:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this, The Pope says\Nto a homeless guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Stay outta my sight, you're\Nan eyesore." You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,0:02:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up and drive, you moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired, I'm tired, I'm tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.67,0:03:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I stuck playing\Nerrand boy with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Dutch! I hope he dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to work on the boat.\NBenny's working on the mechanics.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. Revy's just lying around\Nin her room. Take her with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take Revy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.06,0:03:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's not gonna want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an issue you two\Nneed to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.57,0:03:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with me, or the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start with the closer places.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First head to Rowan "Jackpot" Pigeon's\Nplace on Rachiada Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome Rebecca. I thought\Nyou gave up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:04:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've finally decided to work here as\Na dancer for the S&M show, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.54,0:04:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, isn't it, baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break, Rowan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only came here because\Nmy job brought me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna be tied up\Nor tie anyone else up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're as hard to get as always.\NYou're so fine you'd fit either part.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shame. So, what brings\Nyou here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.89,0:04:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... About the goods from the firm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ordered booze for this place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are 1,500 bottles in warehouse\Nfive of the harbor bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, this really helps.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Tax sure has gone up on these!\NI can't stand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, who's that guy\Nstanding over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, him. He's a newbie at our place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.95,0:04:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got nowhere else to go, so we had\Nno choice but to take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.65,0:04:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in for a rough ride, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever need any help,\Nfeel free to come to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:05:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, Rowan. Don't forget\Nabout the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the shipment's gonna be late?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could've told me that by phone,\Nbut you came all the way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell that to Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine. I've gotta finish\Nfifteen of these today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've gotten a part-timer to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is driving me crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a meeting tonight, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.96,0:05:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some idiots are selling drugs without\Npermission. It's such a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey sis, is that in her ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's in her ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. If you hear anything about that,\Nlet me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.94,0:05:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll thank you properly if you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.88,0:05:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, if we hear anything. We'll come\Nagain, sis. Good luck with the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired, I'm tired, I'm tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.29,0:06:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I stuck playing\Nerrand boy with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, one more\Nand we're done. Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Receive firearms on order from Sister\N"PW" Deegan of the Ripoff Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you old bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Rebecca from the Lagoon Company!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you hurry and open up,\Nold bitch! Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! Hello! Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.27,0:06:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hello! Hello! I'll kill you! Hello!\N- Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:06:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too damned loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.58,0:07:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just put those in the shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But these are cleaned items.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. It's what the sister said.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Two Hands, that's the chapel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.62,0:07:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If trash like you walks through there,\Nyou'll be punished by the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here. Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly is a surprise...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.87,0:07:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that Dutchy-boy would send\Nyou on an errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.61,0:07:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not your problem. Do you have\Nthe goods that we ordered, Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. New items from Eastern Europe,\Narriving here by way of Cambodia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Except for one item.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately we're still waiting for\Nthe Arwin 37 revolving grenade launcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't kid around, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We ordered everything through you\Nbecause we need them for the next job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:08:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, we do have the item.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that another customer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is saying they need it immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, as Lagoon is a very good\Ncustomer of ours...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I wouldn't mind handing it over to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it will either have to be a better\Ndeal or a discount on your services.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.53,0:08:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't trifle with us, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you just play this by the book\Nthen everyone will be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.87,0:08:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't wanna count your money\Nwith your feet, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't make idle threats, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist, why don't you bring\NDutchy-boy around?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I have to say.\NThere's nothing else beyond that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move it, Eda, you second-rate gunman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:09:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to teach you how to smoke\Nthrough your forehead?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is very good tea, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yolanda, young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time since I've had tea\Nthat wasn't from a teabag.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this W&M? Or perhaps\NFortnum and Mason?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my. You're very\Nknowledgeable, young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's W&M. I just love tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.17,0:09:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's a flavor that a company...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with dedication and history\Nwill deliver without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock. Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.68,0:09:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true with any company even\Nif the products differ, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see it. What are\Nyou getting at, young man?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean it's also true\Nfor illegal firearms?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.26,0:10:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't have much of a negotiation\Nif you get too hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if I mean drugs? That's what\NI'm talking about, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.91,0:10:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know drugs are being distributed\Noutside the agreed routes lately, Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hotel Moscow and other\Nmafia in the city...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.25,0:10:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...have put a lot of effort\Ninto finding the culprits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.42,0:10:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've looked everywhere\Nthey could think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, the culprits\Nstill haven't been found.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because there's a blind-spot in a\Nplace where they shouldn't have to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, those who can easily cross\Nborders for religious activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These legitimate NGO members...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.80,0:10:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who don't know they're being used as\Ncouriers are being overlooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.61,0:10:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister Eda.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you put the big bags\Nof sheets into the shed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't cleaned items normally\Ntaken to the living quarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:11:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young man. You can't make statements\Nbased on conjecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You make it sound like the stuff's\Ncoming out of this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a hypothesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.43,0:11:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, the number of weapons\Nleaving and entering this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.87,0:11:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...don't match up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to figure out with a little\Nresearch. It is dangerously easy to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.88,0:11:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Lagoon Company is on friendly\Nterms with Hotel Moscow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but we do not necessarily\Nwork together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.79,0:11:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Improve your timing on\Nwhen to say what...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and you'll really take shape. Eda.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a bit rough, but he passes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.41,0:11:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Add the launcher to the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.34,0:11:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.84,0:12:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dutchy-boy has a good eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.91,0:12:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time for mass. I apologize,\Nbut you'll have to be on your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young man. Come visit us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. You got lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the hell outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could learn from that young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do good business by\Njust waving your gun around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.01,0:12:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw man... We should've timed this\Na little better. It's crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.40,0:12:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat before it gets cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:12:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:12:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll feel better if you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.57,0:13:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme the keys. I'll go back alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, I can't get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ought to go back home to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.22,0:13:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not cut out for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.09,0:13:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who invited me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder. Who kept the church\Nfrom becoming a bloodbath?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like that old lady said.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.77,0:13:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't solve everything with a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better watch what you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been this way\Never since the submarine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Is it about that conversation?\N- Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you never to talk about that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna apologize anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I misheard you. I thought I just\Nheard you fucking with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case... I'll say it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not wrong, and I've got nothing\Nto apologize about!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'm saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just stepped on a non-negotiable,\Nnon-defusing, big ass landmine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a real shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask you one last thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I write on your tombstone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Write, "There's no medicine\Nfor violent idiots".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.31,0:14:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.92,0:14:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? There are some things\Nyou can't solve with a gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.61,0:15:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me "Bastard"!\NMy name is Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got that?! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.79,0:15:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had more than enough of this!\NI won't take any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was done kissing\Nmy superiors' asses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.09,0:15:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm at the end of the Earth\Nkissing some woman's ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.86,0:15:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kinda sick joke is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.36,0:15:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You impudent son of a bitch! You're-\N- The name's Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impudent?! Get real, you damn fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?\NYou're an outlaw, a wild pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.27,0:15:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as soon as you open your mouth\Nit's "Money, money, money"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.38,0:15:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you're a villain\Nafter a big prize...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you end up\Nscavenging off of corpses!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a limit to how greedy\Nyou can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.55,0:16:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have any pride\Nin that head of yours?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try and gloss this over\Nyou white-collar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know about me?!\NWhat the hell do you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! A guy like you,\Nwith a sheltered life...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.73,0:16:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can't understand\Nwhat I've been through!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.44,0:16:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. There's no way\NI could know. I'm not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But let me ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.11,0:16:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.98,0:16:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you live,\Nyou'll encounter suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.75,0:16:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.19,0:16:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no intention of\Nunderstanding that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when you can't answer, you\Nconveniently become the tragic heroine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the most cowardly\Nthing about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.53,0:16:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! You're the one\Nlooking at this conveniently!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.93,0:16:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God damn it. This isn't like those cheap\NHollywood picaresque films you admire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:17:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw that! Look around! It's a pile\Nof shit in every direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin Hood doesn't\Nexist anywhere, dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's no Robin Hood,\Nthen become Robin Hood!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a much better way of life\Nthan crying and bitching!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.36,0:17:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Shut up, damn it! I'm serious!\NI'm gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, then do it. Keep running\Naround in circles like a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you kill me here, it'll just prove that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.74,0:17:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I know how to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget, Revy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I'm here. My bosses\Ncalmly cut my life away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To protect their dirty money...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and their place to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you invited me, it was like\Nsomething blew through me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.26,0:18:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I was freed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My life was the rush hour commute,\Nthe fake laughing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.59,0:18:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...lowering my head and risking my life\Nto maintain a good score.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.00,0:18:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fine as long as I had a place\Nto drink and a batting cage to go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, none of that mattered anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who taught me that...\NThe one who invited me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was you, Revy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I'm concerned...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.98,0:18:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is that the woman who taught me this\Nis acting like those who betrayed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.83,0:19:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you mean, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.50,0:19:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell with it. You're a real pain in the ass.\NYou won't live long, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.74,0:19:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're both suffering idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a bigger idiot than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Super idiot.\N- You're pissing me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! Let me take a look at how\Nyou dance around!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey! You two!\N- What the hell do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear someone's making a ruckus in the\Nmarket and it turns out to be you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy. This isn't some prize\Nin a bag of snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting off like that without concern\Nfor who's watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.67,0:19:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put yourself in the shoes of those who\Nhave to put the fire out after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's why you\Ncollect those fat envelopes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your job, Chief Watsap.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not saying don't do it, just do it where\Nno one is gonna see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.01,0:19:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I won't care if you go and kill,\Nor play hide-the-apple for that matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as there's no trouble, I don't\Nhave to cancel my golfing plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:20:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm bringing you in. We've got\Npaperwork to take care of on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.47,0:20:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn engine is giving me trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a cold one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey chief, don't steal our car.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would want that piece of junk?\NPick it up on your way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one thing. Let me ask this,\Nand there will be no more trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which side do you wanna be on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.18,0:21:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am where I'm standing. Nowhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.19,0:21:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock. Give me a light.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.19,0:21:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light? The cop's got the lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.53,0:21:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?\NYou've got one in your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a terrible day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.61,0:21:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.42,0:21:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so tired. I wanna go home and sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.23,0:21:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.52,0:23:18.52,Black Lagoon Next Episode,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10\pos(980,916)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.73,0:23:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be sold\Noff somewhere, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.83,0:23:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world will keep turning\Neven if there's no justice.
